STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Todd Junior LANDIS, Defendant-Appellant. No. 17-1369 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 19, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

A defendant appeals his judgment and sentence for operating while intoxicated and possession of a controlled substance, third offense. CONVICTIONS AFFIRMED; SENTENCING ORDER VACATED IN PART AND REMANDED.

CONVICTIONS AFFIRMED. SENTENCING ORDER VACATED IN PART. REMANDED.
